This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of "Computation and Language" (cs.CL) as it deals with natural language processing and sentence classification. It may also belong to "Machine Learning" (cs.LG) as it proposes a novel neural network architecture. Additionally, it could be categorized under "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI) as it involves the use of machine learning techniques for language processing. "Neural and Evolutionary Computing" (cs.NE) is another possible sub-category as the paper proposes a neural network architecture. Finally, "Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition" (cs.CV) is a less likely but still possible sub-category as the proposed architecture involves feature extraction from input embeddings.
